{"tid":349962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【勁過阿希】台女拒婚　5年後玩夠求復合　毒舌男列十大原因拒絕","createTime":"2017-08-07T02:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T02:49:43.000Z","uid":55462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b878054180c7dac27808a56b2f34f71502b80e16","tid":349962,"uid":55462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"蘇州過後無艇搭，這個道理在戀愛方面亦適用。前日商台節目《早霸王》中，女聽眾Lucy希望主持森美和小儀可以代她向相識8載的Bosco表白，不過驚爆男方已婚兼有子女，令森美也驚訝地說「勁過阿希」。在台灣，有網民亦分享類似故事，指一名女子曾以年輕未想結婚為由拒絕男友求婚；5年後，女方向前男友表白求復合，但男方毒舌地列舉10大原因拒絕，當中包括「妳的心很醜，身體也很髒，我不想要得病」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/736581/xlarge/9810437bb353acc7a035d93309131a43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F736581%2Fxlarge%2F9810437bb353acc7a035d93309131a43.jpg&h=84dcccd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/736571/xlarge/6a0ad71a7df1083c1e7a1f3741af9c27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F736571%2Fxlarge%2F6a0ad71a7df1083c1e7a1f3741af9c27.jpg&h=5804cabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/736572/xlarge/4c80e048a5009b3afdd85de607e241a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F736572%2Fxlarge%2F4c80e048a5009b3afdd85de607e241a4.jpg&h=ca1f97ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/736573/xlarge/dc2789c7e245cb0a4473334abe5dce59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F736573%2Fxlarge%2Fdc2789c7e245cb0a4473334abe5dce59.jpg&h=758b7491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/736575/xlarge/532e40d21b069d13e7f3b651f5fd0c65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F736575%2Fxlarge%2F532e40d21b069d13e7f3b651f5fd0c65.jpg&h=dec3c07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<